{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"fdbb7b3c-55fb-41c4-bb6b-c344d65af780","content":"Your `.testsettings` file configures three things that need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file (MSTest v3 dropped `.testsettings` support):\n\n| `.testsettings` setting | MSTest v3 equivalent |\n|---|---|\n| `TestTimeout = 30000` | `<MSTest><TestTimeout>` in `.runsettings` |\n| Code coverage data collector | `<DataCollectors>` in `.runsettings` |\n| Assembly resolution / `useLoadContext` | No longer needed — MSTest v3 runs from the output directory by default |\n\nHere's the replacement `.runsettings` file:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"tooluse_m62s8mjjgkoDqEIfWbQY6r","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-a52dcb3b09194d70b10a53832e208d55/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n  </MSTest>\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n        uri=\"datacollector://Microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n        assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.CoverageCollectorDataCollector, Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b03f5f7f11d50a3a\">\n        <Configuration>\n          <CodeCoverage />\n        </Configuration>\n      </DataCollector>\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-a52dcb3b09194d70b10a53832e208d55/local.runsettings."}],"interactionId":"e38e8b85-5f0e-4501-b02d-86c12eefc0a5","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a `.testsettings` file that configures:\n1. Assembly resolution with `useLoadContext=\"true\"`\n2. Test timeout of 30000ms (30 seconds)\n3. A code coverage data collector\n\nIn MSTest v3, `.testsettings` files are no longer supported. The migration path is to use a `.runsettings` file instead, and configure timeouts via MSTest attributes or runsettings.\n\nLet me provide the migration guidance:\n\n1. **Test timeout** → Use `[Timeout]` attribute on test methods or configure in `.runsettings` under `<MSTest><TestTimeout>`.\n\n\n2. **Code coverage data collector** → Configure in `.runsettings` under `<DataCollectionRunSettings>`.\n3. **Assembly resolution / deployment** → MSTest v3 runs tests from the output directory by default, so deployment settings aren't needed. The `useLoadContext` behavior is now the default.\n\nI'll create a `.runsettings` file that replaces the `.testsettings` configuration.","outputTokens":721,"requestId":"BD05:26F972:200F224:24728FF:6A07DA36"},"id":"409048c2-b4d1-40b1-a74a-bf3ec3abf05c","timestamp":"2026-05-16T02:45:22.699Z","parentId":"ff590f4e-654b-4ae8-8585-f613faef0c84"}
